<td bgcolor="#CECECE" class="btext" width="100%"><b>Annihilation Interview</b> - <span class=bsmall>posted by  <a class='nNewsMailLink' href='mailto:ice.m@btinternet.com'>ICE.M</a> on Tue 07 August 2001 12:53:45 | <a href="comments.php?section=1&index=329" class=blink>Comments (0)</a></span></td>
