<td bgcolor="#CECECE" class="btext" width="100%"><b>Day of Defeat 1.3b Patch</b> - <span class=bsmall>posted by  <a class='nNewsMailLink' href='mailto:deathwatch@barrysworld.com'>Deathwatch</a> on Wed 01 August 2001 21:50:36 | <a href="comments.php?section=1&index=323" class=blink>Comments (0)</a></span></td>
