<tr>
<td bgcolor="#EEEEEE" colspan=2 class=news>
<table><tr><td valign=top><img src='images/icon_general.gif' alt='General News' border=0></td><td width="100%" valign=top>Another patch that got released today was <a href="http://www.dayofdefeatmod.com" class=colourise>Day of Defeat</a>'s 1.3b patch. This patch fixes several bugs in this Half-Life World War 2 mod.<br><br><span class=quote>- redone spawn speed system<br>- fixed bandaging cheat<br>- fixed prone speed cheat<br>- fixed mp_friendlyfire<br>- fixed sprites showing `black box` on some cards<br>- fixed transparency of explosions<br>- new explosion sprites<br>- new weapon sounds<br>- other new sounds<br>- updated dod_snowtown<br>- updated dod_cherbourg readme<br>- hopefully the last update before beta 2!</span><br><br>You can download it from Fileplanet either as <a href="http://www.fileplanet.com/index.asp?file=56262" class=colourise>upgrade from 1.3</a> or as <a href="http://www.fileplanet.com/index.asp?file=62053" class=colourise>full installer</a>. For more mirrors, check out the <a href="http://www.dayofdefeatmod.com" class=colourise>Day of Defeat site</a>.<br><br>If you are experiencing some weird problems on your server:<br><span class=quote>"We have complaints of weird prone and crouch speeds and other abnormalities. These did indeed turn up in testing but these are due to admin and meta mod.Make sure that Admin mod, Meta mod or any other program that replaces the dod dlls is uninstalled before installing this patch, and then reinstalled. Failure to do so will result in strange bugs. If you do this everything should run fine!"</span></td></tr></table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
