<td bgcolor="#CECECE" class="btext" width="100%"><b>Operation Flashpoint Patch</b> - <span class=bsmall>posted by  <a class='nNewsMailLink' href='mailto:deathwatch@barrysworld.com'>Deathwatch</a> on Wed 01 August 2001 21:16:12 | <a href="comments.php?section=1&index=322" class=blink>Comments (0)</a></span></td>
<td bgcolor="#CECECE" width=17><img src="images/item_icon.gif" width="17" height="17" alt="" border="0"></td>
