<td bgcolor="#CECECE" width=17><img src="images/item_icon.gif" width="17" height="17" alt="" border="0"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td bgcolor="#EEEEEE" colspan=2 class=news>
<table><tr><td valign=top><img src='images/icon_general.gif' alt='General News' border=0></td><td width="100%" valign=top>Over on <a href="http://www.homelanfed.com/" class=colourise>HomeLAN</a> they have posted <a href="http://www.homelanfed.com/index.php?id=1069" class=colourise>an interview</a> with David Solari of CodeMasters, the company that published Operation Flashpoint.<br><br>The interview covers various subjects, such as why the game was released in Europe first, the upcoming patches and what they are doing in terms of marketing.</td></tr></table>
